The **jellyfish**, ;, is a [sea monster](/wiki/Sea_monster "Sea monster") in [NetHack](/wiki/NetHack "NetHack"). It is extremely slow and does not pose a significant threat.

Jellyfish

From NetHackWiki
Jump to navigation Jump to search
; Jellyfish
Difficulty 5

; Jellyfish
Difficulty 5
Attacks

Bite poisonous 3d3

Base level 3
Base experience 34
Speed 3
Base AC 6
Base MR 0
Alignment 0 (neutral)
Frequency (by normal means) 0 (Not randomly generated)
Genocidable Yes
Weight 80
Nutritional value 20
Size Small
Resistances Poison (20%)
Resistances conveyed Poison

A jellyfish:

  • can swim.
  • can survive underwater.
  • cannot pick up items.
  • has no limbs.
  • has a serpent body.
  • is poisonous to eat.
  • does not eat. (*)
  • is normally generated hostile.
Reference monst.c#line2604
